reliance,standalone,Hedging Reserve,"(16,123)","(26,895)",CORRECTED,"p99 standalone SOCIE Cash Flow Hedge closing = opening (14,090) + (12,805) = (26,895); prior GT (16,123) was an OCI-movement/garble figure, inconsistent with consolidated which correctly uses SOCIE closing (26,919)"
