reliance,standalone,Non Current Investments_Unquoted Debentures/Bonds,Not disclosed,"1,105",CORRECTED,"p127-128: unquoted debentures (excl subsidiaries) = JV-cos [BAM DLR Mumbai 40 + BAM DLR Network 2 + DXDC 63 = 105; Sintex Twenty Devind 900] + Other-co Mahan Energen 100 = 1,105. Prior GT 205 missed Sintex Twenty Devind 900"
reliance,consolidated,Non Current Investments_Unquoted Debentures/Bonds,Not disclosed,"15,162",CORRECTED,"p147(pr.212-213): ALL 'In Debentures or Bonds - Unquoted' lines = Amortised Cost 100 + FVTOCI 201 + FVTPL 13,828 + Associates 4 + JV 1,029 = 15,162. Prior GT 100 captured only the amortised-cost line (instrument-first convention: debentures datapoint = all unquoted debentures across bases/relationships)"
reliance,standalone,Non Current Investments_Joint Venture/Partnerships,Not disclosed,"4,798",CORRECTED,"p127-128: all JV holdings at cost excl debentures = JV equity [quoted Alok 269 + unquoted 979] + JV preference [Alok NCRPS 3,300 + Alok OCPS 250] = 4,798. Prior GT 3,300 captured only NCRPS preference, missing JV equity (1,248) and OCPS (250)"
reliance,consolidated,Non Current Investments_Joint Venture/Partnerships,"9,648","8,619",CORRECTED,"p147(pr.213): JV equity 4,741 + JV preference 3,878 = 8,619 (instrument-first: JV debentures 1,029 belong to the debentures datapoint, not here). Prior 9,648 was the printed JV total which double-counts the 1,029 debentures"
